userdoc.notice: Contract implements mechanism of crowd funding services - allows anybody create CrowdFund contract and collect money for any goal.Events are keeping track of current funding state. Modifiers are protecting from withdrawing funds before fundraising ends.When fundraising phase is over then users can withdraw their funds if goal is not reached, otherwise funds are sent to presetted receiver.
